<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1> For all your Workout needs </h1>
</div>

<div id="indexCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="carousel-item active">
      <img class="d-block w-100 h-50" src="images/Lifting1.jpg" alt="Weightlifting">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-dark text-white">
        <h2>Weights</h2>
        <a href="/Weights">Record a weights workout</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block w-100 h-50" src="images/Running1.jpg" alt="Running">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-dark text-white">
        <h2>Running</h2>
        <a href="/Running">Record a run</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block w-100 h-50" src="images/Swimming1.jpg" alt="Swimming">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-dark text-white">
        <h2>Swimming</h2>
        <a class="text-left font-weight-light" href="/Swimming">Record a swim</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block w-100 h-50" src="images/Biking1.jpg" alt="Biking">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-dark text-white">
        <h2>Biking</h2>
        <a href="/Biking">Record a bike</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block w-100 h-50" src="images/Custom.jpg" alt="CustomWorkout">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-dark text-white">
        <h2>Custom</h2>
        <a href="/CreateYOwn">Record a custom workout</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#indexCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  </a>
  <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#indexCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  </a>
</div>
<br>
<div class="jumbotron">
  <h2> Some Important Health Information: </h2>
</div>

<div class="accordion" id="indexAccordion">
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="indexAccordion-headingOne">
      <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#indexAccordion-collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="indexAccordion-collapseOne">
        How Long Should I exercise for?
      </button>
    </h2>
    <div id="indexAccordion-collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="indexAccordion-headingOne">
      <div class="accordion-body">
        The CDC recommends that adults get "at least 150 minutes of moderate-intensity aerobic physical activity or 75 minutes of vigorous-intensity physical activity, or an equivalent combination each week."
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="indexAccordion-headingTwo">
      <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#indexAccordion-collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="indexAccordion-collapseTwo">
        Healthy Exercise Habits
      </button>
    </h2>
    <div id="indexAccordion-collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="indexAccordion-headingTwo">
      <div class="accordion-body">
        A good workout involves both a Warm-Up and a Cool-Down, don't just jump into a full speed workout from the start, that is just asking for injury. Likewise take the time after a workout to let your body calm back down to it's normal state. Warming Up and Cooling Down will both help you avoid injury in the long run.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="indexAccordion-headingThree">
      <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#indexAccordion-collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="indexAccordion-collapseThree">
        Hydration and Diet
      </button>
    </h2>
    <div id="indexAccordion-collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="indexAccordion-headingThree">
      <div class="accordion-body">
        It is essential to remain hydrated when working out, otherwise you can inflict serious harm on yourself. Also remember eat nutritiously and at regular intervals to put yourself in the best possible position.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="indexAccordion-headingFour">
      <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#indexAccordion-collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="indexAccordion-collapseFour">
        Remember to Pace Yourself
      </button>
    </h2>
    <div id="indexAccordion-collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="indexAccordion-headingFour">
      <div class="accordion-body">
        Remember that nobody achieves all their goals for working out in a single day, much less a single workout. Remember where you're starting from and don't overexert yourself. Also be sure to rest when you need to and take off-days as necessary.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="indexAccordion-headingThree">
      <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#indexAccordion-collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="indexAccordion-collapseFive">
        Last but not least!
      </button>
    </h2>
    <div id="indexAccordion-collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="indexAccordion-headingFive">
      <div class="accordion-body">
        Have fun while exercising!
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

